    "With each level of the convolution layer, the quantity of filters doubles.",
    "This fundamental idea underlies the architecture of VGG16.",
    "The VGG16 model is greater than 533MB due to its depth and quantity of completely connected layers.",
    "Because of this, building a VGGNet is a gradual task.",
    "Many Deep Learning image classification issues use the VGG16 model, however, simpler network topologies like GoogleNet and SqueezeNet are frequently chosen."
